  "keyFeatures": [
    "Real-time single email verification with syntax, MX, and SMTP checks",
    "Async bulk verification of up to 10,000 emails per request",
    "Disposable email detection",
    "Role-based email detection (info@, support@, etc.)",
    "Catch-all domain flagging",
    "Confidence score (0–100) with machine-readable sub-status reasons",
    "Webhook notifications on bulk job completion",
    "Bounce feedback webhook to improve accuracy over time",
    "MCP (Model Context Protocol) server for AI agent integration",
    "Credits that never expire with transparent pay-as-you-go pricing",
    "Sub-500ms average response time with 99.9% uptime SLA",
    "Code examples in Python, Node.js, PHP, Ruby, Go, and Java"
  ],
